name: aurèce's b1k3
description: This is a old bike, lovingly restored on which aurèce vettier strolled many parisian streets. A bike on which a poem is written. Now, it can be yours, and this might be the first NFT listing of a regular bike (Apr 8th 2021). On the first sale, you are entitled to receive it -shipping worldwide. For the secondary sales, aurèce vettier advises to keep shipping the bike and to make sure the poem remains on the frame. After acquisition, DM @aurecevettier for shipping details. AV-2021-U-113
